; E126 - continuation line over-indented for hanging indent (aligned assignment)
; E201, E202 - whitespace after and before parentheses
; E221 - multiple spaces before operator (aligned assignments)
; E241 - multiple spaces after ':' (alignment of dictionary keys)
; E271 - multiple spaces after keyword (aligned imports)
; E302 - expected 2 blank lines, found 1 (single empty line in between methods)
; E302 - expected 2 blank lines, found 1 (single empty line after method/class definition)
; W504 - line break after binary operator
